{"tid":975611,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"叫女朋友明確拒絕厹行為 算唔算唔信過分","createTime":"2019-01-09T19:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-12T12:21:49.000Z","uid":72186,"like":349,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"6d18b3b978e35fefbd71e5005b6a553965144fe6","tid":975611,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:35:46.000Z","msg":"話說<br />\n啱啱同女朋友講話佢成日都有啲唔同嘅人send心心呀 錫錫呀 或者 啲肉麻嘢畀佢<br />\n佢就同我講<br />\n佢ignore咗佢哋 扮睇唔到就算<br />\n當然我絕對信任自己女朋友 但有人send依啲畀佢 自己個心都唔係幾好受<br />\n好似有種默許班厹嘅行為咁<br />\n佢哋一直send一直send<br />\n<br />\n跟住我就話<br />\n希望佢可唔可以明確啲拒絕佢哋<br />\n同佢哋講 可唔可以停止再send依類嘢 <br />\n唔想自己男朋友誤會之類<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢接受咗我做法<br />\n但佢覺得我唔信任佢<br />\n我講完自己感受同做法之後<br />\n就到佢唔開心<br />\n<br />\n自己都有啲自責<br />\n我咁做算唔算過份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔過份<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過份<br />\n<br />\n如果過份 可唔可幫手鬧一鬧我<br />\n我都唔想自己女朋友唔開心<br />\n唔過分 我都想知點做先好"},{"pid":"eb6af81eb2e01813ff7875e750ce13db6aca4642","tid":975611,"uid":104017,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:36:54.000Z","msg":"逝去的<br />\n留不住"},{"pid":"a61ec242a034c9cbeca86087b1117eda8a523643","tid":975611,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb6af81eb2e01813ff7875e750ce13db6aca4642","tid":975611,"uid":104017,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:36:54.000Z","msg":"逝去的<br />\n留不住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:39:21.000Z","msg":"大c 即係點"},{"pid":"c4db852eab803471b47e02c7d486add828759f1b","tid":975611,"uid":104017,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a61ec242a034c9cbeca86087b1117eda8a523643","tid":975611,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb6af81eb2e01813ff7875e750ce13db6aca4642","tid":975611,"uid":104017,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:36:54.000Z","msg":"逝去的<br />\n留不住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T19:39:21.000Z","msg":"大c 